{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"content_hash":"7e149fac92477ab394420368576eab87df6ac1eacd21529eb6a1c8a003c5ba93","digest":{"component_or_area":"creation-channel provenance across CREATE ingress paths and reducer/compaction","key_entities":["creation_channel","creation_channel_inferred","src/rebar/_commands/composer.py:create_core","src/rebar/_engine/rebar_reconciler/apply_inbound_records.py","_ensure_inbound_assignee_identity","ensure_identity_for","create_identity_core","src/rebar/reducer/_version.py","LEGACY_JIRA_AUTHOR","LEGACY_JIRA_ENV_ID","reducer/_processors.py","process_edit","_IMMUTABLE_EDIT_FIELDS","_project_legacy_creation_channel","inbound_translate._event_meta","common.schema.json","ticket_state.schema.json","rebuild_snapshot_from_full_log","cli/mcp/python/jira/import/unknown"],"problem_keywords":["creation channel provenance","immutable audit dimension","ingress attribution","event-sourced create metadata","legacy jira inference","compaction durability","snapshot replay","additive schema contract","reducer immutability guard"],"propositions":["Ticket state does not record which ingress interface (cli, mcp, python, jira, import) produced the original CREATE event, forcing debugging via mutable tags and call-stack inference.","A closed creation_channel vocabulary must be recorded immutably on the genesis CREATE event by each live producer at its entry boundary, defaulting python for direct Python and overriding to mcp/jira/import at their seams.","Legacy records without the field project jira with creation_channel_inferred=true only when the exact three-signal predicate matches (jira- id prefix, author and env equal to LEGACY_JIRA constants), otherwise unknown.","The reducer must treat creation_channel and creation_channel_inferred as CREATE/SNAPSHOT-only state, with process_edit and specialized processors refusing to overwrite them after genesis.","Compaction, SNAPSHOT-only replay, and snapshot rebuild must preserve the exact channel and inference marker, with old-style SNAPSHOT omission recoverable from permanently retained .retired CREATE sources.","Outbound Jira bind/sync operations and NDJSON import must not rewrite genesis provenance; import records its own channel while retaining source_* provenance."]},"digest_hash_version":1,"model":"claude-opus-4-8","schema":"ticket_digest_v1"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"TICKET_DIGEST","timestamp":1784314003862801001,"uuid":"cd156d8f-c3b9-4ba6-9f61-60b1187a3ef7"}